{"_id":"1ZBDDMgWMMWAfOld","name":"Blood Magic","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The character channels her arcane power through an evil or malevolent source, or<br />has learned to draw power through the pain and misery of others.</p>\n<p><br />Every time the mage causes a Wound to a conscious, sapient being of some sort (and<br />the Wound isn&rsquo;t Soaked), she recovers a d6 Power Points. The caster must cause the<br />damage directly, using her Powers, bare hands, weapons, and so on. She gains no<br />benefit from indirect harm such as that caused by a puppeted foe, ally, zombie, pet,<br />or minion.</p>\n<p><br />Those suspected of practicing such tainted magic are often hunted by local<br />authorities. Sometimes there are entire orders dedicated to their eradication. When<br />caught, the sentence is almost always slow, painful, and fatal.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Arcane Background (Any), an evil disposition"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ndbQsQwkkGMcpXta"},"cf":{"id":"temp_y0bdbtf8jfd"}}}
{"_id":"23GKDQieE4Z4eLz2","name":"Warband","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Legendary leaders attract dedicated fighters to their side. Each time this Edge is taken, five of the champion&rsquo;s Followers gain the @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-specialabilities.Resilient]{Resilient} Monstrous Ability.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Wild Card, Legendary, Command and at least two other Leadership Edges, Followers"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.K4rUxS2PfwU3JcFB"},"cf":{"id":"temp_ult6pu9nb1"}}}
{"_id":"2Mh8kwdbpPLhtfMA","name":"Home Ground","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>There are few things more dangerous than a druid in her home forest, a wizard in his lair, or a necromancer in the ruined city his undead horde have built for her.</p>\n<p>Working with the Game Master, designate one area as your hero&rsquo;s &ldquo;home.&rdquo; This might be an entire forest, bay, coastline, or lake and its surroundings for a druid, a church and the small town it serves for a cleric, a tower and its environs for a wizard or elemenalist, or a keep full of contraptions and chemicals for an alchemist or tinkerer.</p>\n<p>Once per encounter, while within this area, the character may spend a Benny to recover all her Power Points. The mage also has a sense of her home, no matter how distant she may be. She may concentrate for ten minutes (one minute if on her Home Ground) to ask three questions about the current, observable state of her homeland, revealed through scrying, visions, or other eldritch sense.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Wild Card, Legendary, Spirit d8+, Arcane Background (Any)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.yGpoDWe8y3GxUCfQ"},"cf":{"id":"temp_ult6pu9nb1"}}}
{"_id":"3418Cu4aMYOhkhjj","name":"Silent Caster","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The character has learned how to cast spells or invoke miracles without speaking.<br />She may cast underwater, in a vacuum, while gagged, or within a silence spell or<br />similar ability.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Arcane Background (Druid, Elementalist, Illusionist, Necromancer, Priest, Shaman, Sorcerer, or Wizard), Occult d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.QgNxCxcCG7PNnoxM"},"cf":{"id":"temp_y0bdbtf8jfd"}}}
