{"_id":"Aj0C92Uj1Uby1SUg","name":"Arcane Background (Wizard)","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The classic spellcaster of any fantasy campaign if the wizard. She might be an apprentice fresh from a magical academy, an aged mage who learned her craft by trial and error, or someone gifted from birth with eldritch affinity.</p>\n<p>Wizards have the largest spell selection of all the Arcane Backgrounds, but no inherent special abilities, and no access to critical powers such as healing or relief.</p>\n<p>ARCANE SKILL: Spellcasting (Smarts)</p>\n<p>STARTING POWERS: Detect/conceal arcana, dispel, lock/unlock, and three other powers chosen from the list below.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>POWER POINTS: 15</p>\n<p>AVAILABLE POWERS: Arcane protection, polymorph, barrier, beast friend, blast, blind, bolt, boost/lower Trait, burrow, confusion, conjure item, curse, damage field, darksight, deflection, detect/conceal arcana, disguise, dispel, drain Power Points, elemental manipulation, empathy, environmental protection, farsight, fear, fly, growth/shrink, havoc, illusion, intangibility, invisibility, light/darkness, lock/unlock, luck/unlock, locate, mind reading, mind wipe, mystic intervention, object reading, planar binding, plane shift, protection, puppet, scrying, shape change, sloth/speed, slumber, smite, speak language, stun, summon ally, telekinesis, teleport, time stop, wall walker, warrior&rsquo;s gift, wish, zombie.</p>\n<p>MAGIC: Wizards may take Edges that require Arcane Background (Magic).</p>\n<p>ARMOR INTERFERENCE (Major): Bulky armor interferes with the precise patterns they must make when working their magics. They subtract 4 from Spellcasting rolls and Agility and Agility-based skill rolls if using light, medium, or heavy armor or shields.</p>\n<p>COMPONENTS: Wizard spells require various bits and baubles, such as gemstones or powders, giving them the Material Components Hindrance (see page 28).</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d6+, Spellcasting d4+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Y9nu0cOySftX5r54"},"cf":{"id":"temp_3666mrdr5op"}}}
