{"_id":"NhJ62wbDk7sK4BoJ","name":"Missile Deflection (Homebrew rules)","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The hero&rsquo;s ability with in melee combat is unparalleled. As long as she can see the missile coming, physical ranged attacks (arrows, axes, powers with physical<br />Trappings, etc.) directed against her (and assuming he can see it coming) use her<br />Parry as the base TN.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fighting d10+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tjAslEPFLn2qHCRO"},"cf":{"id":"temp_q3rzfx4a0po"}}}
{"_id":"NnyzTZ6dwVacZVxY","name":"Martial Flexibility (Homebrew rules)","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Once per encounter, as a free action, the fighter can choose to gain the benefits of a<br />single Combat Edge (@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.o3VbC2xAXHb8RfEN]{Swade Core Edges}). She must meet all of the Edge&rsquo;s Requirements, and the benefits<br />of the chosen Edge end after *[three] rounds.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>*playtesting this part of the rule</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fighting d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.xi9Fb51YczfDBPQO"},"cf":{"id":"temp_q3rzfx4a0po"}}}
{"_id":"O1lQcaNl4mCeCJ6R","name":"Wing Gust","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>he character&rsquo;s wings are powerful enough to knock others down. Gusting is<br />a limited action that requires an Athletics roll. On a Critical Failure, the flyer has<br />over-exerted himself and takes a level of Fatigue. If successful, characters within a<br />Cone Template originating from the hero must make a Vigor roll or be Shaken (at &ndash;2<br />with a raise). If the hero&rsquo;s Action Card is a Joker or she&rsquo;s currently under the effects<br />of Conviction, those who fail are Stunned instead!</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Wings, Seasoned"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.G0CiPnFrB0Q3ZLMo"},"cf":{"id":"temp_q3rzfx4a0po"}}}
{"_id":"O6tTl8TNjhHQbTv2","name":"Phenomenal Power","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>This works exactly like Great Power but allows the sorcerer to spend Conviction to cast any spell available in the setting. (He still adds his Conviction bonus to the roll as well.)</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Heroic, Arcane Background (Sorcerer)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.EmkCvdA5PG9TT1dg"},"cf":{"id":"temp_rqglz4nku8c"}}}
{"_id":"OWDIdurgQpQhzckk","name":"Arcane Background (Cleric)","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Clerics draw their power from a divine presence of some sort, including gods, nature, spirits, or their revered ancestors. They invoke miracles from these entities by reciting prayers or performing rituals they believe are in their deity&rsquo;s best interests.</p>\n<p>A cleric&rsquo;s particular service depends on the deity he serves. A list of &ldquo;domains&rdquo; the Game Master can assign to a particular source of power can be found on page 100 of the Fantasy Companion.</p>\n<p>ARCANE SKILL: Faith (Spirit)</p>\n<p>STARTING POWERS: Healing, sanctuary, and three other powers from their chosen Domain (see page 100).</p>\n<p>POWER POINTS: 10</p>\n<p>AVAILABLE POWERS: Choose a domain from those listed on pages 100 through 101 or create your own based on the world and the divine beings that watch over it.</p>\n<p>MIRACLES: Clerics may take Edges that require Arcane Background (Miracles).  HOLY SYMBOL: Clerics who openly display a symbol of their deity or religion get a free reroll on all Faith rolls.</p>\n<p>VOW: Clerics must have a Vow (Major) to their deity or religion. If they fail to uphold their deity&rsquo;s values, they subtract 2 from Faith rolls for a week. Truly sacrilegious acts might rob them of their powers entirely until they atone in some way.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Spirit d6+, Faith d4+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5jqoZLUUvFWma2mS"},"cf":{"id":"temp_vrmmp54bah"}}}
{"_id":"OdZ28bm94Zb6pr13","name":"Savagery","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Violence is a way of life for some. Those with this Edge hit their foes hard enough<br />that they often don&rsquo;t get to reply in kind.</p>\n<p>A character with this Edge causes +4 damage when making a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Wild Attack]{Wild Attack} rather than +2.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Fighting d6+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.VR9t5mew0jbSiuTf"},"cf":{"id":"temp_9hfm5sf8y2i"}}}
{"_id":"OfzXbiN3LvlJA7MV","name":"Beast Talker","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The character can speak to and understand a general class of animals: birds, marine animals (fish, crustaceans, etc.), insects, mammals, reptiles, etc.</p>\n<p>She doesn&rsquo;t control them, but can attempt to persuade them to help or provide whatever information creatures of their type might understand. The GM should impose appropriate modifiers when conversing with pets, hostile or skittish animals, predators, or those animals who have been hunted or preyed upon.</p>\n<p>The vocabularies, memories, and comprehension of such creatures are limited by their type&mdash;a dog knows and understands far more than a fish, for example. The nature of the world may also define how much its animals understand.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wjxK0FEnQQ9vMr8p"},"cf":{"id":"temp_d3m3ewwj98g"}}}
{"_id":"OrPjOONUPosmL4AT","name":"Roar","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Powerful lungs, magical ability, or great size allow the being to issue a great, bone-<br />shaking roar! As a limited action, the character can make an Intimidation Test<br />in a Cone Template. All targets within are affected and must resist separately.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Spirit d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.wmLGXuQZAAZHHAi7"},"cf":{"id":"temp_q3rzfx4a0po"}}}
{"_id":"PAqjc86gepzP3YIn","name":"Charge","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>A short burst of speed adds significant impact to this hero&rsquo;s melee damage. If she<br />runs at least 5&rdquo; (10 yards), she adds +2 to the damage of her first Fighting attack that<br />turn. This may be combined with a Wild Attack.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Fighting d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.RaYHlKd2kzH6Xzrh"},"cf":{"id":"temp_q3rzfx4a0po"}}}
{"_id":"PW5OAOMRrfSDNmHu","name":"Born in the Saddle","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>There&rsquo;s no place this warrior would rather be than on the back of a fast horse or other,<br />more exotic mount.<br />A hero with this Edge gets a free reroll on all Riding rolls and increases her mount&rsquo;s<br />Pace by 2 and their running die one step.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Agility d8+, Riding d6+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.XhkzhPQX5ruZgevM"},"cf":{"id":"temp_3wjknv5js85"}}}
