{"_id":"X8qXgBHcRAZRVyXV","name":"Power Pool","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Characters can have multiple Arcane Backgrounds with the Game Master&rsquo;s<br />permission, though each has its own set of powers and Power Points.</p>\n<p><br />This Edge lets the hero combine Power Points from two or more different arcane<br />skills into a single pool. A hero with 10 points in both magic and miracles, for<br />example, could combine them into a single 20 point pool that both may draw from.</p>\n<p>Power Points from the Mystic Powers Edge may not be pooled.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, two Arcane Backgrounds (Any), both arcane skills at d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.pN7tluAMFKhfJP4Q"},"cf":{"id":"temp_y0bdbtf8jfd"}}}
{"_id":"Xsz9jMRIibHTNmyJ","name":"Uncanny Reflexes","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The character has an uncanny ability to avoid area attacks and effects. She ignores<br />the usual &minus;2 Agility penalty when making @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Evasion]{Evasion} attempts. She also gets a regular Evasion attempt against area effect attacks or effects that don&rsquo;t usually allow it (at the usual &minus;2 penalty) such as burst or blast, or even confusion or similar spells cast with the Area Effect modifier.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Veteran, Agility d8+, Athletics d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.igjw0wWb60uwcqTU"},"cf":{"id":"temp_aaj2lub9yud"}}}
{"_id":"XxDirkOdwrKyTVaf","name":"Deadly Illusion","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The caster may take the Deadly Power Modifier for their illusions at no additional Power Point cost.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Illusionist), Spellcasting d10+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.MNsqUb2d9XvKdZ5w"},"cf":{"id":"temp_omqixfvb2mh"}}}
{"_id":"YT79O6hyODgN7WVR","name":"Transfer","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The mage, priest, or other practitioner of the arcane arts can give his magical<br />energy to others. As a limited free action, the character may transfer up to five of his<br />Power Points to anyone else in sight.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Arcane Background (Any)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.8SWfZiPIcYriSJj7"},"cf":{"id":"temp_y0bdbtf8jfd"}}}
