{"_id":"cMEJDpeqcDUvDYYs","name":"Improved Close Fighting","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Close fighters target vital areas and weak spots for quick, lethal kills. The<br />attacker adds a bonus to his Fighting roll equal to his enemy&rsquo;s Reach +1.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Close Fighting"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.URgANEeKG8N58y20"},"cf":{"id":"temp_9hfm5sf8y2i"}}}
{"_id":"cyYEvf8QFqH2pRE6","name":"Arcane Background (Necromancer)","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Those who practice necromany learn how to blur the line between the worlds of the living and the dead. Loathed by most, necromancers nevertheless relish in the great power conferred on them by death&rsquo;s dark energy.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>EDGE: Arcane Background (Necromancer)</li>\n<li>ARCANE SKILL: Spellcasting (Smarts)</li>\n<li>STARTING POWERS: Detect/conceal arcana, dispel, zombie, and two other powers chosen from the list below.</li>\n<li>POWER POINTS: 10</li>\n<li>AVAILABLE POWERS: Arcane protection, banish, barrier, blind, bolt, boost/lower Trait, confusion, darksight, deflection, detect/conceal arcana, dispel, divination, drain Power Points, empathy, entangle, farsight, fear, fly, havoc, healing, intangibility, invisibility, light/darkness, lock/unlock,mind link, mind reading, mind wipe, object reading, protection, relief, resurrection, sloth/speed, slumber, smite, sound/silence, stun, summon undead, telekinesis, teleport, wall walker, warrior&rsquo;s gift, zombie.</li>\n<li>MAGIC: Necromancers may take Edges that require Arcane Background (Magic).</li>\n<li>CORRUPTION: Necromancers deal in the dark magic of unlife. They have the Corruption Hindrance.</li>\n<li>RAISE THE DEAD: Zombie is a Novice-Rank power for necromancers and the Duration is increased to four hours.</li>\n</ul>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":true,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Smarts d6+, Spellcasting d4+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.alPdo9MfWzzG7yot"},"cf":{"id":"temp_f045umf8w76"}}}
