{"_id":"t86ZMzjwdCJAqfWo","name":"Stonecutting","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Those who spend their lives around worked stone quickly perceive imperfections or<br />alterations within its design. Assuming they can see or feel the work, they get one<br />free Notice roll at +2 to detect traps, hidden doors, or compartments in stonework<br />within 10 feet of their person. Success means they know some alteration has been<br />made, and a raise gives them insight into its general purpose.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Repair d6+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.bZxxoPktt2JSCVxV"},"cf":{"id":"temp_3wjknv5js85"}}}
{"_id":"tFYWVwjF1hBYwawE","name":"Poisoner","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The character is an expert with poisons. She creates poisons in half the time. In<br />addition, her contact poisons last 12 hours rather than four.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice; Alchemy, Healing, or Survival d6+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.bamo3H8wNqLu9Hre"},"cf":{"id":"temp_rtqi0xm40m"}}}
