{"_id":"uG9Y1Ly1Zvj7iPYx","name":"Mount","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>The hero has a horse or similar sized mount that is more clever than most and<br />utterly loyal to its master (even if it seems cantankerous or otherwise disagreeable).<br />Increase the mount&rsquo;s Smarts by one and give it the Loyal Hindrance (to its master<br />only) and the Resilient Monstrous Ability.</p>\n<p>Death: If the mount perishes, another takes its place eventually, perhaps after a long narrative trek or several encounters that describe how the beast and rider bond.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Riding d6+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.Y3Tzy6rUah9uJksz"},"cf":{"id":"temp_3wjknv5js85"}}}
{"_id":"uhq22iaHGxPSuc3u","name":"Inspire Heroics","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Bards inspire their comrades with epic tales of valor and bravery. Once during any combat encounter (GM&rsquo;s call), the bard can spend a Benny to gain five Inspiration tokens. This is a limited free action.</p>\n<p>For the remainder of the encounter, the bard may give these tokens to anyone within a Range of Smarts except himself. This may be done at any time (as long as the bard is conscious). The recipient must use the token immediately&mdash;it cannot be saved.</p>\n<p>Each Inspiration token allows a character to reroll a Trait or damage roll. A Trait or damage roll may only benefit from a single Inspiration Token, even if there are multiple bards present. Further rerolls require spending a Benny or a special ability.</p>\n<p>Inspiration tokens aren&rsquo;t Bennies, don&rsquo;t trigger Edges that use Bennies (such as Elan), and can&rsquo;t be used as such in any other way such as drawing new Action Cards or Soaking Wounds.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Bard), Performance d8+"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.x5LrR6HkMZXcv8NV"},"cf":{"id":"temp_2jnavlrmj8e"}}}
{"_id":"ulRHE0368gWlxhdo","name":"The Witching Hour","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Witches and warlocks are more powerful between the hours of midnight and 1 am (or some other suitable time in your campaign world). During this hour, a witch or warlock cannot Critically Fail a roll (it&rsquo;s just a normal failure), and gets a free Soak roll anytime she takes a Wound!</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Seasoned, Arcane Background (Warlock/Witch)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.i7lsXAxoP6Zlsj3T"},"cf":{"id":"temp_b0alwhlbt6"}}}
{"_id":"vHqeRDvweVUmCqOm","name":"Heartwood Staff","type":"edge","img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/edge.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Some druids focus their powers through a staff made from rare wood, such as the heart of a great oak or the last palm from a dying desert oasis.</p>\n<p>If such a staff is lost or broken, the druid must spend at least eight hours in an old forest with at least a few trees a hundred years old or more. There she may make a Faith roll at &ndash;2 once per day to forge another. This sacrifices the tree it&rsquo;s taken from.</p>\n<p><br />HEARTWOOD STAFF:<br />Str+d8, Min Str d6, Weight 6 lbs., Parry +1, Reach 1, requires two hands.</p>\n<p>After the druid hits with the staff, she may spend a Power Point to cause an extra d6 damage. This die may Ace.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"favorite":false,"isArcaneBackground":false,"requirements":{"value":"Novice, Arcane Background (Druid)"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"0llfus6nG1V829T5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5g8rVoExOdTqF4TG"},"cf":{"id":"temp_xkxhv65se9e"}}}
